    <PrimAttribute name="actAsReleasePoint" id="7dc19974-ceef-423b-89e8-05f745b7faf1">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>This is a bit mapped field (well, at the moment its treated as a bool)
but its intended purpose is to be flagged up as a release point for cams/output/
checking only type of stuff.
Used currently (in 1999) to check the suitability to release
for some areas in the yard. Only some areas have this set, those areas are the ones that
are NOT normally release points (like an LCL pack area)</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
