        <source>isTransferArea() : Boolean;
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:     11 July 2002 by cnwdf1
//
// Purpose:     
//
// Parameters:  None
//
// Returns:     Nothing
//
// Changed On   Changed By  Reason
// ----------   ----------  --------------------------------------------------
// 31/08/2009	cnwcs5		ccms 1061 - gate config changes
